First off you are the slower, so having a slower about is no problem.  Second, this sounds like the result of powerleveling.  However, the best way to raise defense is to do chanter like things:<br>
<br>
- Tash<br>
- Mezz<br>
- Slow<br>
- Stun<br>
- occasionally nuke<br>
<br>
No matter what your MA is you should be able to grab aggro if you feel like it.  Now your healer is going to have to be on the ball because 50s chanters are a fragile lot (unlike 60s chanters).<br>
<br>
At the end of the day your AC (the thing Defense will raise) is pitiful anyway.  You are going to get maxed most of the time by mobs (you also have poor mitigation - comes with the class).<br>
<br>
But at the end of the day, chanters are the casters in the middle of the melee fight (desirable or not).  Get in there take and take some hits.  (Wait till your tripled and proced in PoV or quadded in BoT for the first time - there mobs don't just sing it they bring it.)<br>
